ust have strong\ntwo-fold in-plane anisotropy. These findings are consistent with a\nFermi-surface reconstruction caused by a unidirectional spin-density wave or\nstripe order.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2010 19:13:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 16 Feb 2011 09:39:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-17"}
