y cadence,\nphotometric variability provides an even better method than color selection for\nseparating quasars from stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Sep 2010 19:29:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Dec 2010 19:31:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-01-28"}
